body:
Can you attach an example that shows the issue?  (Must be openly licensed, ideally in test_regress format.)

VCS (on EDA playground) errors out:
```
Error-[SV-TNVVM] Task not visible via modport
testbench.sv, 14
$unit, "v_if.reset"
  Task 'reset' of interface 'example_if' cannot be accessed from instance 
  'v_if' of modport 'driver'.
  To access the task from the modport instance, import or export the task in 
  the modport prototype.
```

```
// Copyright 2003 by Wilson Snyder. This program is free software; you
